<div class="faq-page-wrapper" style="background-color: #fafafc; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; padding: 80px 0; min-height: 100vh;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px;">

    <!-- Title Header -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
      <span style="color: #FF2B2B; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em;">Help & Support</span>
      <h1 style="font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; color: #111; margin: 0; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">Everything you need to know about formula use, shipping timelines, and returns.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Categorized FAQ Items -->
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">
      
      <!-- FAQ Accordion 1 -->
      <div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e9e9eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.01);" class="faq-item">
        <button type="button" onclick="toggleFaqAccordion(1)" style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: none; border: none; padding: 24px 32px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; outline: none;" id="FaqBtn1">
          <span>Are your cleaning formulas safe for all shoe materials?</span>
          <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #FF2B2B; transition: transform 0.3s ease;" id="FaqIcon1">&plus;</span>
        </button>
        <div style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); padding: 0 32px;" id="FaqContent1">
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; padding-bottom: 24px; margin: 0;">Yes. Our elite formula is high in organic cleaning agents, making it fully pH-neutral and 100% safe for canvas, nylon, vinyl, rubber, mesh, premium leathers, and suedes. When cleaning delicate napped leathers like nubuck, we recommend using our Premium Suede Brush gently.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Accordion 2 -->
      <div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e9e9eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.01);" class="faq-item">
        <button type="button" onclick="toggleFaqAccordion(2)" style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: none; border: none; padding: 24px 32px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; outline: none;" id="FaqBtn2">
          <span>How long does the Shield Guard protective coating last?</span>
          <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #FF2B2B; transition: transform 0.3s ease;" id="FaqIcon2">&plus;</span>
        </button>
        <div style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); padding: 0 32px;" id="FaqContent2">
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; padding-bottom: 24px; margin: 0;">Once correctly applied and cured for 24 hours, our nano-technology shield repels water, mud, and stains for up to 4 to 6 weeks under normal daily wear. For optimal durability, we recommend a touch-up application once a month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Accordion 3 -->
      <div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e9e9eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.01);" class="faq-item">
        <button type="button" onclick="toggleFaqAccordion(3)" style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: none; border: none; padding: 24px 32px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; outline: none;" id="FaqBtn3">
          <span>How long does standard delivery take?</span>
          <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #FF2B2B; transition: transform 0.3s ease;" id="FaqIcon3">&plus;</span>
        </button>
        <div style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); padding: 0 32px;" id="FaqContent3">
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; padding-bottom: 24px; margin: 0;">All orders placed before 12pm CET are shipped the same business day. Delivery times within Western Europe range between 2 to 4 business days. International delivery takes approximately 5 to 9 business days.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Accordion 4 -->
      <div style="background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e9e9eb; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.01);" class="faq-item">
        <button type="button" onclick="toggleFaqAccordion(4)" style="width: 100%; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: none; border: none; padding: 24px 32px; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #111; cursor: pointer; text-align: left; outline: none;" id="FaqBtn4">
          <span>What is your returns and refund policy?</span>
          <span style="font-size: 20px; color: #FF2B2B; transition: transform 0.3s ease;" id="FaqIcon4">&plus;</span>
        </button>
        <div style="max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); padding: 0 32px;" id="FaqContent4">
          <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; padding-bottom: 24px; margin: 0;">We offer a 30-day trial period on all cleaning kits. If for any reason you're not absolutely satisfied with the results, contact our support team to request a full, no-hassle return label and 100% refund.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<style>
  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .faq-page-wrapper {
      padding-top: 48px !important;
      padding-bottom: 48px !important;
    }
    .faq-page-wrapper [style*="font-size: 42px"] {
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 7vw, 2.25rem) !important;
    }
    .faq-item button span:first-child {
      flex: 1;
      padding-right: 8px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  function toggleFaqAccordion(id) {
    const content = document.getElementById('FaqContent' + id);
    const icon = document.getElementById('FaqIcon' + id);
    
    if (content.style.maxHeight && content.style.maxHeight !== '0px') {
      content.style.maxHeight = '0px';
      icon.innerHTML = '&plus;';
      icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
    } else {
      content.style.maxHeight = content.scrollHeight + 'px';
      icon.innerHTML = '&minus;';
      icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
    }
  }
</script>
